OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,FThe cause of deaths of three sisters
OL,8,Fwho were recovered from the sea off
OL,9,FBrighton beach is "yet to be
OL,10,Fascertained", an inquest has heard.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called after
OL,13,Fconcerns were raised for a person's
OL,14,Fwelfare at around 5.45am on May 13,
OL,15,Fbefore three bodies were pulled from
OL,16,Fthe water near Madeira Drive.
OL,18,FThe women were named by Sussex Police
OL,19,Fas Jane Adetoro, 36, Christina
OL,20,FWalters, 32, and Rebecca Walters, 31,
OL,21,Ffrom the Uxbridge area of London.
OL,26,@qD@SOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
