OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,FAn inquest which opened at Woodvale in
OL,8,FBrighton on Friday, heard post-mortem
OL,9,Fexaminations had offered a provisional
OL,10,Fcause of death as "yet to be
OL,11,Fascertained".
OL,13,FSenior coroner Penelope Schofield told
OL,14,Fthe women's father Joseph Jacobson,
OL,15,Fwho attended the hearing online, that
OL,16,Fthe loss of his daughters must be
OL,17,F"unbearable", and she offered
OL,18,Fcondolences.
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@LO]yD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,FStatements read to the inquest
OL,8,Fdetailed that Ms Adetoro was brought
OL,9,Fto shore by an RNLI crew and declared
OL,10,Fdeceased by a paramedic at the scene.
OL,12,FChristina Walters was recovered from
OL,13,Fthe sea by an RNLI lifeboat and
OL,14,FRebecca Walters was washed on to the
OL,15,Fshore of Brighton beach. Both were
OL,16,Falso declared dead by paramedics.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,FThe inquest heard "medical
OL,8,Finvestigations are ongoing to finalise
OL,9,Fthe cause of death" for all three
OL,10,Fwomen, but at this stage police are
OL,11,Fsatisfied there was no third party
OL,12,Finvolvement.
OL,14,FIt was heard the sisters lived at the
OL,15,Fsame address in Greenford, west
OL,16,FLondon, and their occupations were
OL,17,Funknown.
OL,26,@oD@SOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,FThe coroner said she hoped the details
OL,8,Ffrom the hearing would "stop social
OL,9,Fmedia speculation" around the
OL,10,Fcircumstances of their deaths, and
OL,11,Fadjourned the inquest to be heard on
OL,12,FOctober 8.
OL,14,FFollowing their deaths, their father
OL,15,FMr Jacobson said there are days when
OL,16,Fthe grief feels "unbearable", but he
OL,17,Fholds on to the memories they shared
OL,18,Fand "the bond that death can never
OL,19,Ftake away".
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@RO]xD@QOUxD@\O]zD@EOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,FIn a statement released through Sussex
OL,8,FPolice, he said: "Jane, Christina and
OL,9,FBecky were more than daughters to me;
OL,10,Fthey were my joy, my strength, and the
OL,11,Fbeautiful light that filled our family
OL,12,Fwith happiness and love.
OL,14,F"Each of you was unique and precious
OL,15,Fin your own special way. Your smiles
OL,16,Fbrightened dark days, your laughter
OL,17,Fbrought comfort, and your presence
OL,18,Fmade life more meaningful.
OL,26,@pD@ROUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,F"Though your time on earth was short,
OL,8,Fthe impact you made will remain in our
OL,9,Fhearts forever."
OL,11,FA GoFundMe page set up by the family
OL,12,Ffor funeral costs and support has
OL,13,Fraised nearly #44,000.
OL,15,FSussex Police have said there is no
OL,16,Fevidence to suggest criminality or
OL,17,Fthat anyone else was involved in the
OL,18,Fincident, but specialist detectives
OL,19,Fare working to gather the full facts
OL,20,Fand circumstances around their deaths.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780071066
OL,3,CCause of deaths of three sisters
OL,4,Crecovered from sea off Brighton as yet
OL,5,Cunknown
OL,7,FHundreds of hours of CCTV footage have
OL,8,Fbeen reviewed and inquiries made to
OL,9,Fbusinesses and properties around the
OL,10,Fbeach area to try to track the women's
OL,11,Flast movements, the force has said.
OL,13,FChief Superintendent Adam Hays has
OL,14,Fsaid the force "will leave no stone
OL,15,Funturned" in the investigation to
OL,16,Funderstand what led to the "tragic
OL,17,Fevents of that Wednesday morning".
OL,26,@vD@POUwD@IO]xD@\OUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
